=== Cambiar el idioma ===

To [[localization|localize]] KDE Applications, enable the <code>nls</code> USE flag to automatically pull in the necessary packages, either globally in {{Path|/etc/portage/make.conf}} or just for the relevant meta packages:

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/package.use/kde-apps-nls|title=Setting the <var>nls</var> USE flag per package|lang=bash|1=
kde-apps/kde-apps-meta nls
kde-apps/kdepim-meta nls
kde-apps/plasma-telepathy-meta nls
}}

If only a select few languages are desired, define the <var>L10N</var> variable in {{Path|/etc/portage/make.conf}}. E.g. to use the German language, set:

{{FileBox|filename=/etc/portage/make.conf|title=Setting the <var>L10N</var> variable for the German language|lang=bash|1=
L10N="de"
}}

{{Note|To put these [[USE_flag]] changes into effect, a rebuild of the above list of packages is required.}}

To '''manually''' install these localization packages, use the following (complete) list or pick as desired:

{{Emerge|kde-l10n kde4-l10n kdepim-l10n ktp-l10n}}

La aplicación {{Package|app-office/calligra}} tiene su propio paquete de localización también: {{package|app-office/calligra-l10n}}.

